            <div type="transcript" id="F314B">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>&quot;Hope&quot; is the thing with<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 feathers -</l>
                    <l>That perches in the soul - </l>
                    <l>And sings the tune without<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 the words - </l>
                    <l>And never stops - at all - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>And sweetest - in the Gale -<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 is heard -</l>
                    <l>And sore must be the storm - </l>
                    <l>That could abash the<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 little Bird </l>
                    <l>That kept so many warm - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>I've heard it in the chillest<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 land - </l>
                    <l>And on the strangest Sea -</l>
                    <l>Yet - never - in Extremity, </l>
                    <l>It asked a crumb - of me.  </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
